resources.string:
"XThemeEngine themes uses a format similar to CM10 themes. XThemeEngine supports theming of resources except those in assets folders (i.e. ringtones, wallpapers) and styles.xml.
Howto/Support: https://plus.google.com/communities/107334160991587538620 Follow @ruqqq for updates: http://twitter.com/ruqqq
WARNING: This is a beta app. It comes with no warranty or guarantee!"
